  "text": "In order to verify the algorithm, the analysis of simulation signal was performed. The mathematical expressions of the simulation signal are as follows: [CITATION_1] where f 1 (t) f 2 (t) f 3 (t) represent the components at three different frequencies, and f (t) represents the composite signal consisting of the first three signals. The EMD method and EWT method were used to process the simulation signal. The used simulation signal and its frequency spectrum are presented in Figures 1 and 2 , respectively. In addition, the obtained decomposition results of the EWT and EMD are shown in Figures 3 and 4 , respectively.",
